Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:08.58,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:11.26,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We're going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.79,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I will stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.73,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,If someone doesn't hold them back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.23,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,win or lose, we'll all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:25.46,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. If I'm at a disadvantage, I will run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.83,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Shogen-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:30.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go, Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:31.17,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.10,Bullet_Ep_Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,420)}#04 Black Bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.40,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.29,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.78,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.57,Bullet_Main,shogen,0000,0000,0000,,Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.13,Bullet_Main,shogen,0000,0000,0000,,My sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuma Shogen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:41.54,Bullet_Main,shogen,0000,0000,0000,,Have you... seen my sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.64,Bullet_Main,shogen,0000,0000,0000,,As long as... I have that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.77,Bullet_Main,shogen,0000,0000,0000,,I can... still... fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.27,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.82,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,He really is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.26,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,The end is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.82,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Let us finish this, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.99,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,With the civil officers we have \Nin the vicinity, it'd take even
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.81,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the closest pair at least an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.97,Bullet_Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.22,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,I called for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:25.54,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,President Tendo, what would you say is the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.17,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,success rate for the Satomi pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.23,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,If I may voice my own expectation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:31.72,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,they will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.58,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:36.47,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,What? They're up against the survivor \Nof the New Humanity Creation Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.56,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,They don't stand a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.61,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:43.63,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Gastrea came into my house \Nand devoured my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.87,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the stress I endured at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.67,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,my kidneys are barely functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:53.04,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, Satomi Rentaro protected me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:57.88,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Gastrea took his right hand, \Nright leg, and left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:01.72,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,On the verge of death, \Nhe was taken to Section 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:04.64,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,The performing surgeon was Dr. Muroto Sumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.50,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Muroto Sumire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:08.81,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.81,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You will not retrieve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.23,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.19,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,We stand in your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,A second defeat, \Nthe annihilation of my comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:26.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I couldn't have asked for \Na better situation, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I will eliminate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo Martial Arts First Style, Number 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.49,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,He broke through Maximum Pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.34,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Artificial limbs made from Varanium?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.45,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you're also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce myself, as well, Kagetane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:13.08,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I am formerly from the Ground \NSelf-Defense Force's Eastern Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:17.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,787th Mechanization Special Unit, \Nof the New Humanity Creation Plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.40,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,There was another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.21,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Another of the human weapons \Nborn of the Gastrea War?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.04,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I am in pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.47,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I am alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.02,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,What a magnificent life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.85,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.27,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mean to Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.17,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Cry, Sodomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.24,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Sing, Gospel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:05.05,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,We were created to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:08.03,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,If the Gastrea War were to recommence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.98,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the significance of our lives will be proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me... \Nthat's the reason you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.61,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,What did the people around you think
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:21.03,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,when they found out your Initiator \Nwas one of the Cursed Children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.17,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Did they offer their blessings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.48,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Were you touched by endless cheers of joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:30.56,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,The world that we wish for \Nis different from theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.59,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,We have been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.21,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Satomi Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:38.00,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:41.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.23,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.00,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I can accept the future you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.65,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.92,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot abide...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:59.31,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Then die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.53,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:18.04,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Am I... going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.05,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:28.05,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro! Please do not leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:37.06,Bullet_Flashback,sumire,0000,0000,0000,,The AGV experimental drug was \Ncreated from the Gastrea virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.31,Bullet_Flashback,sumire,0000,0000,0000,,It gives humans the regenerative \Nabilities of the Gastrea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:45.94,Bullet_Flashback,sumire,0000,0000,0000,,but there is a 20% chance that they \Nwill turn into Gastrea themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.53,Bullet_Flashback,sumire,0000,0000,0000,,If you can avoid it, don't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.23,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I won... that gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:28.52,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:35.03,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo Martial Arts Suiten Ippeki Stance:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Unebiko Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.35,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Inzen Kokutei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.39,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Am I... going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:01.27,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,lose to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.98,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,Papa... Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.37,Bullet_Main,ops,0000,0000,0000,,Hiruko Kagetane's signal has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.51,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.13,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:42.16,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,No... No, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.50,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.96,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,She's no longer an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.86,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I won like I promised, Kisara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.40,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.00,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,But, Satomi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.16,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some bad news I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.37,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,A Stage Five Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.26,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,has shown itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything over?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.15,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let it end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.17,Bullet_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Seitenshi-sama has given her consent to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.68,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is to the southeast of your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.93,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Ladder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.56,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to do it, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.12,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,The Linear Electromagnetic Projectile Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.23,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as Heaven's Ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.68,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,A railgun module that fires metallic projectiles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:27.02,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,with a diameter less than \N800 millimeters at near light speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.41,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,If we shoot Varanium rounds at a speed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:34.57,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that would make regeneration impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:39.26,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,we'd be able to exterminate \Neven a Stage Five Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:46.01,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing operation of the \NLinear Electromagnetic Projectile Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.62,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Power supply, nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.89,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Dewar vessels for liquid \Nhelium storage, also nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.80,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.54,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of the launch sequence here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.15,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as everything is operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.93,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,So all we have to do now is watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:02.15,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't do anything, \Neven if they told us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.74,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Stage Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.84,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The Zodiac Gastrea: Scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.45,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Gastrea that almost \Ndestroyed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.50,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.87,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,It's displaying a message saying \Nthere's a problem in the chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.59,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:59.31,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible the Varanium \Nrounds haven't been loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.50,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! There aren't any rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.16,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0000,0000,0000,,Electrical power preservation system \Ncoolant leak confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.39,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0000,0000,0000,,Please halt the experiment at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.39,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.01,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the magnetic field...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:21.41,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, it's not responding \Nto remote commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.04,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.79,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro, you aren't going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:43.09,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use my right arm as a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be an issue \Nif it's super Varanium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.76,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0000,0000,0000,,Varanium charge detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.06,Bullet_Main,ops,0000,0000,0000,,We can't regain control \Nof the launch sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:57.76,Bullet_Main,ops,0000,0000,0000,,Without doing it manually on-site, \Nlaunch is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.23,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.00,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fire the railgun from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.73,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Please! You have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:07.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:12.34,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, the world— Please—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.00,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara-san! Kisara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.21,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0000,0000,0000,,Energy levels at 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.50,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0000,0000,0000,,Initiating manual trigger system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.51,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:43.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to manually hit a \Ntarget 50 kilometers away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.57,Bullet_Main,kisara,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.57,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.14,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro, I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.84,Bullet_Main,rentaro,0000,0000,0000,,If we miss, we're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.37,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we'll hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:24.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The shell could veer toward the Tokyo Area \Nand cause an unprecedented disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.03,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's you, Rentaro, \Nit'll hit the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.35,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:42.21,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,No one else but you, Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.08,Bullet_Main,rentaro,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.22,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose you, no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:02.65,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,May I interpret that as a proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:03.95,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Take it as me saying you're family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,A ten-year-old shouldn't be talking about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:10.44,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,You're not scared anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.16,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.47,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.97,Bullet_Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.88,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,So you've... found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd run if you \Nwere at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:18:00.39,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-san, how's Shogen-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:03.89,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,He's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.21,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-san... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.53,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The corrosion rate in your body is over 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.97,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me die as a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:31.02,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,As the one who acknowledged my existence, \NI didn't want to let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.99,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:35.30,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.62,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.33,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.59,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,is filled with gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.51,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:19:01.81,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Satomi-san, you don't have \Nvery many friends, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:05.20,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.13,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You are my irreplaceable friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.97,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-san, from here on out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.63,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,If you get lost in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.77,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,follow the compass within your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.14,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,and go towards the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.47,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please save
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.65,Bullet_Main,natsu,0000,0000,0000,,this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.32,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,About the information leaked to Kagetane...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:04.25,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying it was caused by Defense \NMinister Kutsuoda's party going on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.52,Bullet_Main,kiku,0000,0000,0000,,Kutsuoda just hanged himself in \Nhis detainment cell and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.89,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,He worked for you, didn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The New Gastrea Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:19.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,A law that will raise the social \Nstatus of the Cursed Children...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,But you're all for discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.18,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You made it known that his daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.41,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kohina, was involved in this act of terrorism,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,and encouraged animosity \Ntoward the Cursed Children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You even tried to summon a Stage Five Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.78,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that would destroy the Tokyo Area,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.83,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to stop the New Gastrea Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:42.23,Bullet_Main,kiku,0000,0000,0000,,How could you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:47.51,Bullet_Main,kiku,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, those bugs killed \Nmy wife and many others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:53.63,Bullet_Main,kiku,0000,0000,0000,,They also took your arm and leg, \Nand you want me to grant the children
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.81,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,who carry their blood human rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:01.44,Bullet_Main,kiku,0000,0000,0000,,They are the demons who will \Nbring destruction to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls are human...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:07.45,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Satomi Rentaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,believe in Aihara Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:13.23,Bullet_Main,kiku,0000,0000,0000,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.49,Bullet_Flashback,kiku,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not want to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:23.01,Bullet_Flashback,kiku,0000,0000,0000,,survive, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.59,Bullet_Main,rentaro,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in the pit of despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.39,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I would remember those \Nwords and pull through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:34.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I have never forgotten what \Nhappened that day ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.82,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Seitenshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:46.23,Bullet_Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.30,Bullet_Flashback,senten,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.58,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I saw what was inside the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.62,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0000,0000,0000,,A broken-down tricycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:22:00.38,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell is that a catalyst \Nto summon a Scorpion?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.25,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What are Gastrea, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:05.51,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me, Seitenshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.81,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:22.23,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:26.67,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is your arm all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,For the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:32.10,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Did Sumire tell you the results \Nof my corrosion exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:34.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. 24.9%.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:38.99,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it's barely changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:42.42,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.55,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,If the hierarchy were to improve,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:47.42,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,civil officer pairs would \Nbe given special rights:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:49.72,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,A quasi-class elevation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:53.01,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,and the access key to top secret information.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:58.51,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-san, rise through the ranks with Enju-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:05.23,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will know
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:11.05,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,the reason you were born \Nand who you truly are...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:25.63,Corrosion_23:23,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Corrosion Rate \N\N{\b1}42.1%
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:25.92,Aihara_23:23,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,390)}Aihara Enju \N\N{\b0}((Medical Chart))
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:28.46,Corrosion_23:23,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Percentage Until Bodily Breakdown \N\N {\b1}7.2% Remaining
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:40.48,Bullet_Next_Ep_Title,sign,0000,0000,0000,,#05 The Crimson Black Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:32.05,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.50,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bodyguard request.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.80,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro, I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:35.97,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.38,Bullet_Main,voice,0000,0000,0000,,What is your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:40.06,Bullet_Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,The assassination of the Tokyo \NArea representative, Seitenshi.
